list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: Fixed cut and neck_cut to set HB. Fixed a module bug in data_predicates.

task.summary:
Changed version to 1.5.0. Added documentation. Cleaned up tiles.html.
Fixed doc generator to not put empty parentheses on predicates.

Extended data_predicates.pl with undo. Updated version to 1.5.2.
Changed console.pl to use new data_predicates/4. data_predicates.pl: changed to data_predicates/4 from /3 to add 'option' (undoable, ephemeral) argument; added use of undo module; added cuts for performance optimization; added 'action' predicate generation for get, set, update, and clear. Extended object.pl with >>$/2 - this is >>/2 with a trailing cut; added cuts for performance optimization. Added undo.pl to support undoing assertions (primarily of data_predicates data). bootstrap_js.pl: added cuts to partition/4 and key_partition/4 to prevent sort/2 from creating needless choicepoints. Fixed proscript_interpreter_terminal.js to use $.terminal.escape_formatting on strings to be output in the terminal (fixes a bug with strings containing '[[' due to nested lists). Updated JQuery terminal to 2.9.0.

Added WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope interface and random builtins.
Optimized sort/2 to check if the 'input' list is already in sorted order. Added random/1 and random_between/3.

Fixed compare_terms to deref args and handle lists correctly.
Extended keysort/2 with presorted check. Added term compare tests.
Fixed sort check to remove duplicates.

Added some builtin doc. Fixed writeq escape of \.
Added doc for arithmetic comparisons and 'is'/2, term comparisons, atom chars/codes, number codes, char conversion. Fixed quote_atom function in read.js to escape \. Fixed generate_predicate_doc.pl generate_pred_sidenav_entry/2 and generate_pred_cat_sidenav_entry/3 to use writeq for Label and Pred.

Added doc for many predicates. Fixed gensym to increment counter.
Extended generate_pred_cat_sidenav_entry/3 to convert category terms to display strings with '-' replaced by space (' ').
Converted memory refs in foreign.js to always deref, using get_arg.
Converted more memory[VAL(...)...] refs to always deref, using get_arg.
